; Regression test for issue #696: Width options return integers to expressions
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/696
;
; Width options (total_width, amount_width, etc.) must return INTEGER
; values to the expression engine so that arithmetic like `4 + total_width`
; works without requiring an explicit int() cast.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --columns 80 -F "%(4 + total_width)\n"
16
16
end test
